title: addressing your assumptions about us
itunes:title: addressing your assumptions about us
description:
Brooke and Danielle get VULNERABLE today and open the floor up listeners to submit their assumptions about the gals….  The gals discuss these assumptions on everything from finances, to relationships and even their friendship!  The gals also catch up on their weekends, Danielle’s visit to Georgia and talk about the upcoming week with Brooke’s 25 birthday.    Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!
